  "description": "<i>Skarabeusz</i> is a computer adaptation of Scrabble for up to four players, played on a 15x15 grid board. Each player starts the round with seven letters, which may be replaced or placed on the board. Each letter has a certain value. For arranged word the player receives as many points as located on the letters forming the word. Each color on the board has a special characteristics causing doubling or tripling points for letters or arranged words.<br><br>\nAs a free bonus, <a id=\"d24aa8de8581639b44cf2d0367f0b4eb6\" href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Masa+Krytyczna\">Masa Krytyczna</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Kosci+zostaly+rzucone\">Ko?ci zosta?y rzucone</a> are added in the box.",
